Title: Temporal Two-ning
Description:
I see... They are falling through possibilities as well as time.

Hurry, I have located another point in the timeline where we might catch them. It is... unusual, but do not let the strangeness of this world slow you down. Chronormu's fate is in your hands.
ObjectivesText: Use Chrono Crystal on Eternus and Chromie in Azmerloth to stop them from falling through time.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Nozdormu in the Present.
RewardText: The process was not finished but I can more accurately track Chronormu now.
